text: Mimenicodes thomsoni is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Fauvel in 1906. It is known from New Caledonia.BioLib.cz - Mimenicodes thomsoni. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Lamiinae Category:Beetles described in 1906
title: Mimenicodes thomsoni
